<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="card shadow-sm">
    <div class="card-body p-5">
      <h1 class="display-5 mb-4 text-center">About LocalLive</h1>

      <p class="lead text-center mb-4">
        Discover live music happening around you — right now.
      </p>

      <p>
        LocalLive puts nearby venues and live events on a map, so you can find great music without the guesswork.
      </p>

      <p>
        Whether you're into solo acts at a cozy bar or outdoor sets with a crowd, use filters to find the vibe you’re looking for.
      </p>

      <p>
        Artists and venues can create profiles, post events, and grow their audience. Fans can follow favorites and stay in the loop.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-5" />

      <h5>How the map works</h5>
      <p>
        See live events within the next 12 hours near your location. Use filters to explore genres, settings, and more.
      </p>

      <h5>Following artists and venues</h5>
      <p>
        Follow your favorites to filter the map and get updates when they post new shows.
      </p>

      <h5>Own a venue?</h5>
      <p>
        <%= link_to "See how LocalLive helps you bring in music lovers", owners_about_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" %>
      </p>

      <h5>Are you an artist?</h5>
      <p>
        <%= link_to "Promote your shows and connect with fans", artists_about_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" %>
      </p>

      <hr class="my-4" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
